 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">White, <span class="ff20 ws59">Selected Messages,<span class="ff23"> book 1, p. 121. During this week’s lesson, </span></span></div><div class="t m0 x23 h5 y1e0 ff23 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws13">we will explore the role that prayer played in some of the great reviv<span class="ws0">-</span></div><div class="t m0 x23 h5 y1e1 ff23 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws1">als in the Bible. </div><div class="t m0 x3 h5 y1e2 ff20 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws1">*Study this week’s lesson to prepare for Sabbath, July 13.</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
